{"tid":590334,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"降噪耳機","createTime":"2018-03-12T13:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T14:08:29.000Z","uid":79546,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebdef11f27080f9fe7707ce3ca9fa9feef206d8","tid":590334,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"去咗HMV試兩款藍牙耳機<br />\n第一次戴降噪耳機嗰種感覺真係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但經過上網一番蒐集之後發現有人會有頭暈嘅感覺<br />\n有冇巴打介紹下/分享下邊隻好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係試下以下兩隻<br />\nBose Quietcomfort 35 ii<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/214809_05dbcb92a81be23627814aa9981fe3db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F214809_05dbcb92a81be23627814aa9981fe3db.png&h=9c47a390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋Sony WH-1000XM 2<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/214810_63a5e3f4b3965671fddbb97d96e84e18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F214810_63a5e3f4b3965671fddbb97d96e84e18.png&h=c2d6010e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cb159fc1e41e1c9d832eeaa89208328a11dfba5","tid":590334,"uid":66254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:57:05.000Z","msg":"Noise cancelling帶耐咗聽覺好攰"},{"pid":"2e06188cfe82a635df4fcb17675e90e62aad45b0","tid":590334,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"Sony 唔知點解會高分過 Bose .. 不過最近搵搵到大陸既 Linner NC50 (我未比錢都未知係大陸既, 因為鬼佬 Review 講到好得 .. 本來想買 QC30 因為用過 20 同 25 Bose 真係好得)<br />\n<br />\nNC50 最大問題唔知點解用非完廠耳塞會無左降噪<br />\n<br />\n不過 Sony Bose 我寧願信牌子 Bose<br />\n買過 B&amp;O 同 AA 既主動降噪都無 Bose 咁得"},{"pid":"494520fa8355bf5366ae4bcce7002ac0b77e6391","tid":590334,"uid":69749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":